'''衣冠庙站'''位于[[成都市|成都市]][[武侯区|武侯区]]一环路南四段与永丰路交叉口<ref>{{cite news | title = 成都地铁3号线衣冠庙站 部分道路恢复双向六车道通行 | publisher = 凤凰网 | date = 2014-01-20 | url = http://news.ifeng.com/gundong/detail_2014_01/20/33183147_0.shtml | accessdate = 2014-01-20 | language = zh | archive-date = 2017-08-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170818093049/http://news.ifeng.com/gundong/detail_2014_01/20/33183147_0.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>，是[[成都地铁3号线|成都地铁3号线]]的地下[[岛式站台|岛式车站]]，于2016年7月31日启用<ref name="启用">{{cite news  | title = 成都地铁3号线一期工程试运营 熊猫主题列车首发  | publisher = 新浪  | date = 2016-07-31  | url = http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2016-07-31/doc-ifxunuyk4220798.shtml  | accessdate = 2016-07-31  | language = zh  | archive-date = 2016-08-01  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160801212833/http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2016-07-31/doc-ifxunuyk4220798.shtml  | dead-url = no  }}</ref>。因老地名“衣冠庙”而得名。在建设过程中的工程名为“高新大道站”<ref>{{cite news | title = 成都地铁3号线6站点月底开工 2015年成都地铁网建成 | publisher = 四川在线 | date = 2012-04-20 | url = http://sichuan.scol.com.cn/cddt/content/2012-04/20/content_3643515.htm | accessdate = 2012-04-20 | language = zh | archive-date = 2017-08-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170816110700/http://sichuan.scol.com.cn/cddt/content/2012-04/20/content_3643515.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

